    "40884832": {
      "title": "Distances between intuitionistic fuzzy sets",
      "abstract": "A geometrical representation of an intuitionistic fuzzy set is a point of departure for our proposal of distances between intuitionistic fuzzy sets. New definitions are introduced and compared with the approach used for fuzzy sets. It is shown that all three parameters describing intuitionistic fuzzy sets should be taken into account while calculating those distances."
